{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.120", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte G\u00e4ste! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis Ende Mai werden noch Betriebsr\u00e4te gew\u00e4hlt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir diese Debatte auch hier im Bundestag f\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die betriebliche Mitbestimmung ist gelebte Partizipation und Demokratie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.640", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Besch\u00e4ftigten in den Betrieben einmischen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.280", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mitreden und ihre Arbeitswelt aktiv mitgestalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ihre Anliegen geh\u00f6rt werden und wenn sie sich gut vom Betriebsrat vertreten f\u00fchlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann entsteht ein Gef\u00fchl von Wertsch\u00e4tzung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das st\u00e4rkt den Zusammenhalt in unserer Gesellschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen auch wir die Mitbestimmung st\u00e4rken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.280", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben genau die gleiche Debatte schon einmal in der letzten Legislaturperiode gef\u00fchrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten damals einen Antrag eingebracht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke ist damals nachgezogen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es gab eine Anh\u00f6rung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben debattiert,\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und doch ist rein gar nichts in den letzten vier Jahren passiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau das w\u00e4re dringend notwendig; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.920", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die wei\u00dfen Flecken bei der Mitbestimmung sind gro\u00df. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Betriebsratsarbeit wird behindert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wahlen von Betriebsr\u00e4ten werden verhindert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich nicht \u00fcberall, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.200", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Cronenberg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wenn so etwas passiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann muss man etwas dagegen tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Mittel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eingesetzt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.600", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind teilweise heftig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.560", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aktive Besch\u00e4ftigte werden eingesch\u00fcchtert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "benachteiligt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gemobbt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "abgemahnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.520", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ihnen wird teilweise sogar gek\u00fcndigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.960", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das darf nicht sein in einer demokratischen Gesellschaft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.520", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb brauchen die Betriebsr\u00e4te mehr Schutz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei geht es uns Gr\u00fcnen vor allem um drei Aspekte:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.960", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die schwierigste Zeit ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich Besch\u00e4ftigte auf den Weg machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.080", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um einen Betriebsrat zu gr\u00fcnden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und vor allem dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Betriebe das verhindern wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.040", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese aktiven Besch\u00e4ftigten ihr Vorhaben bei einer neutralen Stelle nicht\u00f6ffentlich ank\u00fcndigen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann bekommen sie ab diesem Zeitpunkt den besonderen Schutz nach \u00a7\u00a078 Betriebsverfassungsgesetz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00fcrde die Besch\u00e4ftigten nicht nur vor Benachteiligung sch\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Regelung w\u00fcrde auch ermutigen und motivieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aktiv zu werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.960", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Schummer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.000", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben es vorhin angesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.200", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcbernehmen Sie doch einfach unsere Idee, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.080", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und \u00e4ndern Sie das entsprechend in dieser neuen Legislaturperiode."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.400", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt Branchen und Betriebe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die einen hohen Befristungsanteil aufweisen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.240", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort sind nat\u00fcrlich viele befristet Besch\u00e4ftigte im Betriebsrat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau sie m\u00fcssen h\u00e4ufig als Erste gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.400", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das macht die Betriebsratsarbeit extrem schwierig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und deshalb sollen die befristet Besch\u00e4ftigten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.680", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Betriebsrat sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.840", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den gleichen Schutz wie Auszubildende bekommen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.000", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Arbeit der Betriebsr\u00e4te lebt von Kontinuit\u00e4t."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Betriebsr\u00e4te behindert oder Betriebsratswahlen verhindert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.720", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sind das Straftaten nach \u00a7\u00a0119 Betriebsverfassungsgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.400", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und doch haben Arbeitgeber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die so etwas tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Regel nichts zu bef\u00fcrchten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.600", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geht gar nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.040", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf keine rechtsfreien R\u00e4ume geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier muss endlich etwas getan werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gro\u00dfe Herausforderungen wie die Digitalisierung bew\u00e4ltigen die Unternehmen nur mit engagierten Belegschaften, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Mitbestimmung schafft daf\u00fcr die Voraussetzungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.440", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mitbestimmung bedeutet f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten Mitarbeit auf Augenh\u00f6he im Betrieb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und f\u00fcr die Arbeitgeber entsteht dadurch Vertrauen in der Belegschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.080", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vorteile der Mitbestimmung sind eigentlich bekannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch der Gesetzgeber hat sich beim Betriebsverfassungsgesetz ganz klar positioniert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.040", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da steht n\u00e4mlich nicht \u201esollen\u201c oder \u201ek\u00f6nnen\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.960", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern da steht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.640", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Betriebsr\u00e4te werden gew\u00e4hlt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.640", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und doch wird diese Akzeptanz br\u00fcchig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.560", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb brauchen die Besch\u00e4ftigten Unterst\u00fctzung und R\u00fcckendeckung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.240", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.680", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen Sie bitte zum Schluss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.520", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Regierungsfraktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
